OL,3,CChancellor's local Labour party urges
OL,4,Cher to abandon welfare cuts
OL,6,FRachel Reeves' local Labour party will
OL,7,Fdemand that the Chancellor abandons
OL,8,Fher plans to cut disability benefits.
OL,10,FThe Leeds West and Pudsey Constituency
OL,11,FLabour Party (CLP) has agreed to write
OL,12,Fto her "as soon as possible" to make
OL,13,Fclear it does not support the cuts.
OL,15,FThe local party branch passed a motion
OL,16,Fopposing the cuts, seen by the PA news
OL,17,Fagency, when it met this week.
