OL,3,CChancellor's local Labour party urges
OL,4,Cher to abandon welfare cuts
OL,6,FThe Government's plans, set out in a
OL,7,FGreen Paper earlier this year, would
OL,8,Ftighten the eligibility criteria for
OL,9,Fthe main disability benefit in
OL,10,FEngland, the personal independence
OL,11,Fpayment (Pip).
OL,13,FRestricting Pip would cut benefits for
OL,14,Faround 800,000 people, while the
OL,15,Fsickness-related element of universal
OL,16,Fcredit also set to be cut.
