OL,3,CChancellor's local Labour party urges
OL,4,Cher to abandon welfare cuts
OL,6,FThe package of measures are aimed at
OL,7,Freducing the number of working-age
OL,8,Fpeople on sickness benefits, which
OL,9,Fgrew during the pandemic and has
OL,10,Fremained high since.
OL,12,FThe Government hopes the proposals can
OL,13,Fsave _5 billion a year by the end of
OL,14,Fthe decade.
OL,16,FIn its motion opposing the plans, the
OL,17,FLeeds West and Pudsey CLP said
OL,18,Fdisabled people "are not responsible
OL,19,Ffor the state of the national finances
OL,20,Fand should not be made to pay the
OL,21,Fprice for Tory economic mismanagement".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
